2009-06-05 :
   For classes, functions and variables, names must NOT be used. Instead they
   must be retrieved using an index.

   * vm/Engine : Retype attribute [classes] with t::Classes**
   * vm/Engine : + attribute [unsigned long long classes_n]
   * vm/Engine : + attribute [t::Function** functions]
   * vm/Engine : + attribute [unsigned long long functions_n]
   * vm/Engine : Change call(...) to call using an index
   * Remove vm/ClassTable, vm/ClassTableEntry, vm/FunctionTable and vm/FunctionTableEntry
